    "log": {
      "entries": [
        {
          "key": 0,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "You open your eyes. Straw beneath you, the smell of wet rice, a low roof you do not know. A cold spring — the ninth year of An'ei — though the year is as lost to you as your name.",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 1,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"You're awake.\" Sōan the physician sits back on his heels. \"No kami carried you off, whatever the village wants to believe. A flood took you, and a blow to the head took the rest. Bodies forget. Given work and rice, they also mend.\"",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Sōan",
          "voice": "physician"
        },
        {
          "key": 2,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "You take stock of yourself: bruised, hollow, half-starved — but breathing.",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 3,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "Rice lies scattered across the Kurosawa grain-store floor. Spilled stores are waste — and clearing waste is a kind of work, if you set your hands to it.",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 4,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"Then I'll trust your craft, not the village's ghosts.\"",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "You",
          "voice": "player"
        },
        {
          "key": 5,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"Sense, at last. Rest, eat, and let the swelling go down. The wits come back last — don't force them.\"",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Sōan",
          "voice": "physician"
        },
        {
          "key": 6,
          "channel": "milestone",
          "text": "Perk unlocked — Sōan's Counsel: A mind honed sharper than the body it wears. (+1 INT / −1 STR)",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1
        },
        {
          "key": 7,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "Something surfaces and is gone — a porter's knot, a road in grey rain, a name you cannot keep hold of.",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 8,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"Hold the road. The rain. Almost a name.\"",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "You",
          "voice": "player"
        },
        {
          "key": 9,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "You chase it inward — and the ache in your skull chases you back. The name stays lost, but the habit of looking sets in.",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 10,
          "channel": "milestone",
          "text": "Perk unlocked — The Inward Turn: A mind that deepens by dwelling, at the price of a slower body. (+1 INT / −1 SPD)",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1
        },
        {
          "key": 11,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "On your feet, then. I am Genemon, steward of this house, and I keep the little it has left to keep. You'll not remember any of it, so hear it plain: the Kurosawa are samurai still — on the lord's rolls, if nowhere in the granary.",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Genemon",
          "voice": "steward"
        },
        {
          "key": 12,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"I'll earn my keep. Point me at it.\"",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "You",
          "voice": "player"
        },
        {
          "key": 13,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"...Good. The house has had its fill of hands that don't. We'll see if you mean it.\"",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Genemon",
          "voice": "steward"
        },
        {
          "key": 14,
          "channel": "milestone",
          "text": "Perk unlocked — Genemon's Charge: Honest muscle set plainly to the task — sure over nimble. (+1 STR / −1 AGI)",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1
        },
        {
          "key": 16,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "So you put your hands to it. Rake what grain is still whole back toward the basket, a fistful at a time. We reckon a samurai house’s worth in koku — a year’s eating for one man — and every basket you save us is a measure we need not go begging to the lord to make good.",
          "tick": 0,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Genemon",
          "voice": "steward"
        },
        {
          "key": 17,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "Your arms are leaden. You could rest a moment against the cool post.",
          "tick": 2,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 19,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "Clear it without my standing over you, and you'll have earned your rice and a dry corner to sleep in. I'll make you no grander promise than that. In this house, none of us holds one.",
          "tick": 2,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Genemon",
          "voice": "steward"
        },
        {
          "key": 21,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"...You don't shirk the work,\" Genemon says, eyeing the cleared boards and the filling basket. \"The house has had its fill of hands that do. Earn your keep, and a place here is yours.\"",
          "tick": 4,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 143,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "Dawn at the gate. The forecourt is swept clean — your doing — and Genemon waits by the posts, watching you the way a man watches weather.",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 144,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"You cleared the stores without being told twice. The house is short of hands and shorter of trustworthy ones. Stay — you're no day-hire now. Earn your rice.\"",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Genemon",
          "voice": "steward"
        },
        {
          "key": 145,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"The gate and the swept forecourt are yours to work now; stores come and go here. The home paddies too — the rice that feeds the house. And the kura's own repair is yours to tend: spend the house's small surplus to shore it up.\"",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Genemon",
          "voice": "steward"
        },
        {
          "key": 146,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "A pack-laden stranger has laid a mat in the lee of the gate-post — an Ōmi pedlar, come because a tended gate draws trade. He lifts a hand as you pass.",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 147,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"A tended gate's a lucky gate for a man with a pack. Tokubei, of Ōmi — mind if I keep my mat here a while, young master? Coin of your own spends as well as any lord's.\"",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Tokubei",
          "voice": "villager"
        },
        {
          "key": 148,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"The house has my hands.\"",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "You",
          "voice": "player"
        },
        {
          "key": 149,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"...Good. Hands that don't need watching are the rarest thing I keep.\"",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Genemon",
          "voice": "steward"
        },
        {
          "key": 150,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "The gate and the swept forecourt are yours to work now — stores come and go here.",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 151,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "The terraced home paddies open to you — the rice that feeds the house.",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 152,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "You begin to mark the turning of the days, and the four seasons with them.",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 153,
          "channel": "milestone",
          "text": "Rank ↑ — Kept hand 下人",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "contentKey": "rank.marker",
          "params": {
            "title": "Kept hand",
            "kanji": "下人"
          }
        },
        {
          "key": 154,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "The estate's own state of repair is yours to tend now — spend the house's surplus to shore it up.",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 155,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "The rice you clear and grow is food, not only trade — a plain bowl of it fills a hollow belly and puts you back to work the faster.",
          "tick": 18,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 638,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "The near hill in first light. Genemon leads you past the forecourt for the first time, out to where the woodlot meets the wild edge of the satoyama.",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 639,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"You can be set a task and trusted to finish it out of my sight — worth more than a strong back. The woodlot and the near hill are yours to work now; the house needs fuel and forage, and it trusts you to bring them in.\"",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Genemon",
          "voice": "steward"
        },
        {
          "key": 640,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"One more thing, and not a small one. A wolf's been at the grain stores in the night. Someone must face it — and there is no one else to send. Think on it.\"",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Genemon",
          "voice": "steward"
        },
        {
          "key": 641,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "A lean man about your own age ambles up from the wood-stack, an axe on one shoulder, grinning as if you two already share a joke.",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 642,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"Rokusuke — kept on two winters back, so I know where the bodies are buried. Do the work, keep your head down, don't let the old steward catch you idle. That's the whole of it.\"",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Rokusuke",
          "voice": "villager"
        },
        {
          "key": 643,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "Knotting a load for the woodlot, your fingers tie a porter's knot you never learned — quick, certain, a stranger's habit in your own hands. It means nothing. It will not leave you.",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 644,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"The stores are the house's life. I'll face it.\"",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "You",
          "voice": "player"
        },
        {
          "key": 645,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "\"...Huh. Most men find a reason to be elsewhere. You might do.\"",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "speaker": "Rokusuke",
          "voice": "villager"
        },
        {
          "key": 646,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "A way to track what your hands are learning takes shape — your Skills.",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 647,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "The stable yard and woodlot edge — fuel, timber, and the first sight of the road out.",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 648,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "Above the estate lies the near satoyama — sansai to gather, and the first edge of danger.",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 649,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "Beyond the near hill the ground climbs into the deep satoyama — a richer forage for those who dare it, and the boar in its wallow.",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 650,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "A wolf has been at the grain stores in the night, bold with hunger. Someone must face it — and there is no one else to send.",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 651,
          "channel": "milestone",
          "text": "Rank ↑ — Trusted hand 手代",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "contentKey": "rank.marker",
          "params": {
            "title": "Trusted hand",
            "kanji": "手代"
          }
        },
        {
          "key": 652,
          "channel": "narration",
          "text": "You could boil the wild greens into a hot meal — plain fare, but a warm meal is what closes wounds and mends a body after a fight.",
          "tick": 22,
          "count": 1,
          "voice": "narrator"
        },
        {
          "key": 1189,
          "channel": "reward",
          "text": "Work the home paddies. (+5 rice)",
          "tick": 4,
